# validation.mdc

- Code existing is not completion
- Passing tests alone is not completion
- Validate technical correctness
- Validate product correctness
- Validate architecture correctness
- Never mark work done without verification
- Evidence is mandatory
- Validate releases cumulatively from v0 to target
- Reject execution when rollback safety is missing
